# Quality gates (mandatory)

Every change to this repository must leave the codebase **fully typechecked and linted**. Do not consider a task done until checks pass.

## Required before finishing code work

Run from the repo root (after `uv sync --all-extras` if deps changed):

```bash
make lint
```

That runs:

1. `uv run ruff check src tests`
2. `uv run ruff format --check src tests`
3. `uv run mypy` (strict, package `flex_testing_agent`)

Also run relevant tests:

```bash
make test
```

## Rules

- Fix all ruff and mypy failures you introduce (or that your change surfaces in touched code)
- Prefer `make format` to auto-fix style, then re-run `make lint`
- Do not weaken `pyproject.toml` mypy/ruff settings to silence errors
- Do not skip checks with `# type: ignore` / `# noqa` unless there is a short, justified comment
- New modules under `src/flex_testing_agent/` must typecheck under strict mypy
- Keep tests lint-clean (`tests/` is included in ruff)

If lint or typecheck fails, fix it in the same turn before reporting completion.
